  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/21/garageband-free-ios7/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/garage-band-free-ios7.jpeg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n继 iWork、iPhoto、iMovie 等苹果应用在新 iOS 设备上<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/10/apple-iwork-ios/\">变成免费</a>之后，今天网络上又爆出了音乐制作软件 GarageBand 同样将为 iOS 7 用户提供免费下载的消息。根据 <a href=\"http://www.macrumors.com/2013/10/20/garageband-for-ios-to-become-free-with-in-app-purchases-as-apple-reveals-full-set-of-new-ilife-and-iwork-icons/\">MacRumors</a> 的说法，苹果在近期更新 iLife、iWork 图标的同时，也把 GarageBand 的商业模式调整成了免费下载加应用内购（乐器、音效等）。但老实讲，此举会不会让使用者的开销多过现在 GarageBand 售价还很难说，而更多的细节，Tim Cook 应该会在<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/15/apple-october-22nd-event/\">后天凌晨</a>的发表会上一一道来吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/21/garageband-free-ios7/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.macrumors.com/2013/10/20/garageband-for-ios-to-become-free-with-in-app-purchases-as-apple-reveals-full-set-of-new-ilife-and-iwork-icons/\" target=\"_blank\">MacRumors</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/21/garageband-free-ios7/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20750105/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/21/garageband-free-ios7/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
